content: chandiniv1: Contributed documentation for several plugins with 3 merged PRs, including substantial documentation for the image generation plugin in PR #1591 (+7540/-1200 lines), and READMEs for the ton plugin (PR #1496) and websearch plugin (PR #1494). Additionally has an open PR (#1590) for adding a README for the near plugin, showing a clear focus on improving plugin documentation. Activity was concentrated on just 2 days this month, with all contributions focused on documentation files.
